x4freetext: The C12(p,p)C12 differential cross section
Gas targets of propane (99% purity) and, for some data
at low energies, ethylene.
Two proportional counters used consisted
of an inconel tube 7/4 in. long and 5/8 in. inside
diameter, with a 0.005-in. Kovar wire suspended along
the center axis.
Statistical uncertainty usually <1% and
never more than 2%.
See reference for discussion of other uncertainties.
